  <verse number="28" style="v" />So it is all the more eagerly that I am sending him, so that when you see him again you may rejoice and I will be freer from anxiety.

  <verse number="29" style="v" />Welcome Epaphroditus in the Lord with all joy. Honor people like him.

  <verse number="30" style="v" />For it was for the work of Christ that he came near death. He risked his life to serve me and fill up what you could not do in service to me.</para>
